window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He’s told to save the world. To stop the death of billions. But the only thing he’s given is a chance.</b></p> <p>Jim has saved his clan, but has become a wanted man in the process. His journey toward the capital must continue. He needs to warn the king of the danger his kingdom now faces, and Jim only has the support of his friends. Winter is trying to freeze them to death; the forces of darkness are on high alert; and the monsters are hungry. The hunt is on.</p> <p>Jim must find a way to survive the storm. Even if his team does make it, Jim knows his enemies will be waiting for him to show his face once more.</p> <p>Failure isn’t an option, and Jim only hopes that he can fight through without sacrificing his friends along the way.</p>"; 
